<title>USA: TABLE-Ameristar Casinos sells $100 mln in debt.</title>
<headline>TABLE-Ameristar Casinos sells $100 mln in debt.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-07-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>The following 144a debt issue from Ameristar Casinos Inc was priced Thursday via lead manager Bear Stearns &amp; Co Inc, according to market sources.</p>
<p>Ameristar owns and operates casinos in Jackpot, Nevada and a riverboat dockside casino in Vicksburg, Mississippi.</p>
<p>BORROWER AMERISTAR CASINOS INC</p>
<p>AMT $100 MLN	 COUPON 10.5 PCT   MATURITY 8/1/04</p>
<p>TYPE SR SUB NOTES  ISS PRICE 100     FIRST PAY DATE 2/1/98</p>
<p>LAST MOODY'S B3    YIELD 10.5 PCT    PAY FREQ SEMI-ANNUAL</p>
<p>LAST S&amp;P B-MINUS   SPREAD +425 BPS   CALLABLE NON CALLABLE</p>
<p>							    FOR FOUR YEARS</p>
<p>NOTES: ((THREE-YEAR EQUITY CALL FOR 25 PCT OF ISSUE AT 110.50))</p>
<p>((U.S. Corporate Bond Unit, 212-859-1662))</p>
